title: Modified LaTeX Document with Inserted Figures
description: LaTeX document with all figures successfully inserted at semantically appropriate locations. Contains 10 figures total: 1 motivation figure (in Introduction), 1 algorithm figure (in Method), 5 main_result figures (in Experiments), and 4 ablation figures (in Ablation Studies). All figures have proper captions, labels, and are referenced with \includegraphics commands. The document includes the graphicx package for figure support.
